# AIcademy Environment Variables
#
# HOW TO USE:
# 1. Copy this file and rename the copy to .env (remove the .example)
# 2. Fill in your actual values below
# 3. Save the file
# 4. Never share your .env file or commit it to GitHub — it's already in .gitignore
#
# You can skip this file for now if you're just starting out.
# Cursor's built-in AI handles tutoring without needing your own key.
# Come back to this when you reach Stage 6 (Working with APIs).

# ── OpenAI ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get your key at: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# Used for: AI-powered problem generation and grading scripts
OPENAI_API_KEY=your-openai-key-here

# ── Anthropic (optional) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get your key at: https://console.anthropic.com/
# Used for: Claude-based tutoring scripts (alternative to OpenAI)
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-anthropic-key-here
